          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 0.38+-6 mg/cm**2 thick CD(2) target was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The carbon-induced background was determined in a",
                "dedicated run using a pure carbon target. This",
                "component,normalized to the number of C nuclei in the",
                "CD(2) target and the number of incident particles,",
                "accounts for the negative excitation energy part of the",
                "Ar-45 spectrum and Ar-41 spectrum was presented."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "2FR GAN"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " GANIL/SPIRAL facility"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "PRJFS"
                ],
                "institute": "2FR GAN"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The Ar-44 nuclei were produced by means",
                "of the fragmentation of a 66-MeV/A primary beam into a",
                "thick carbon target. The Ar nuclei were extracted from",
                "the target heated and were purified and accelerated to",
                "an energy of 10 MeV/A by the CIME cyclotron.",
                "For checking and calibration purposes, a stable beam",
                "of Ar-40 was accelerated to an energy of 11 MeV/A in",
                "a dedicated setting."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " One multiwire proportional chamber (MWPC) CATS",
                "was used for determination the (x,y) position of the",
                "reaction on target, on an event-by-event basis.",
                "The MWPC also served to monitor the beam intensity.",
                "The efficiency of the MWPC has been determined relative",
                "to a plastic scintillator located behind the CATS",
                "detector. The deduced efficiency is 95.(5)%."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The outgoing proton was detected at backward",
                "angles in one of the eight modules of the double-sided",
                "silicon strip detector. Each module has a active area",
                "of 60*60 mm**2, divided into 60*60 perpendicular strips"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The transfer-like residues were selected and",
                "identified by the GANIL energy-loss spectrometer(SPEG)",
                "The detection system consisted of two cathode readout",
                "drift chambers, an ionization chamber and plastic",
                "scintillator."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Quoted errors on excitation energies include",
                "statistical errors, propagated uncertainty on the",
                "energy calibration of the detectors-approx. 30 keV,",
                "and the uncertainty on the reconstructed angle of",
                "emission of the proton approx. 50 keV.",
                "Cross section uncertainties arise from statistics,",
                "background normalization, thickness of the CD(2)",
                "target, incident number of particles and geometrical",
                "efficiency."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
